panels.description: Percentual de chamados resolvidos dentro do SLA de 24h

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  COALESCE(
    ROUND(
      (COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) FILTER (WHERE EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (c."encerradoEm" - c."geradoEm")) / 3600 <= 24)::numeric / 
      NULLIF(COUNT(DISTINCT c.id), 0) * 100), 2
    ), 0
  ) as "SLA 24h"
FROM chamados c
LEFT JOIN usuarios u ON c."usuarioId" = u.id
LEFT JOIN ordens_de_servico os ON c.id = os."chamadoId"
WHERE c."encerradoEm" IS NOT NULL
  AND $__timeFilter(c."geradoEm")
  AND ('${tecnico:csv}' = '' OR c."tecnicoId" = ANY(string_to_array('${tecnico:csv}', ',')))
  AND ('${servico:csv}' = '' OR os."servicoId" = ANY(string_to_array('${servico:csv}', ',')))
  AND ('${setor:csv}' = '' OR u.setor::text = ANY(string_to_array('${setor:csv}', ',')));

panels.description: Tempo médio de resolução diário vs meta SLA de 24h

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  DATE_TRUNC('day', c."encerradoEm") as time,
  'Tempo Médio' as metric,
  ROUND(AVG(
    EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (c."encerradoEm" - c."geradoEm")) / 3600
  )::numeric, 1) as value
FROM chamados c
LEFT JOIN usuarios u ON c."usuarioId" = u.id
LEFT JOIN ordens_de_servico os ON c.id = os."chamadoId"
WHERE c."encerradoEm" IS NOT NULL
  AND $__timeFilter(c."encerradoEm")
  AND ('${tecnico:csv}' = '' OR c."tecnicoId" = ANY(string_to_array('${tecnico:csv}', ',')))
  AND ('${servico:csv}' = '' OR os."servicoId" = ANY(string_to_array('${servico:csv}', ',')))
  AND ('${setor:csv}' = '' OR u.setor::text = ANY(string_to_array('${setor:csv}', ',')))
GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('day', c."encerradoEm")

UNION ALL

SELECT 
  DATE_TRUNC('day', c."encerradoEm") as time,
  'Meta SLA 24h' as metric,
  24.0 as value
FROM chamados c
WHERE c."encerradoEm" IS NOT NULL
  AND $__timeFilter(c."encerradoEm")
GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('day', c."encerradoEm")

ORDER BY time ASC;

panels.description: Detalhamento dos chamados ativos no sistema

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  c.id as "ID",
  c."OS" as "OS",
  SUBSTRING(c.descricao, 1, 50) as "Descrição",
  c.status as "Status",
  COALESCE(t.nome || ' ' || t.sobrenome, 'SEM TECNICO') as "Técnico",
  u.setor::text as "Setor",
  STRING_AGG(DISTINCT s.nome, ', ') as "Categorias",
  ROUND(
    EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (NOW() - c."geradoEm")) / 3600::numeric, 1
  ) as "Tempo Aberto (h)",
  TO_CHAR(c."geradoEm", 'DD/MM/YYYY HH24:MI') as "Criado Em"
FROM chamados c
LEFT JOIN usuarios t ON c."tecnicoId" = t.id
LEFT JOIN usuarios u ON c."usuarioId" = u.id
LEFT JOIN ordens_de_servico os ON c.id = os."chamadoId"
LEFT JOIN servicos s ON os."servicoId" = s.id
WHERE c.status IN ('ABERTO', 'EM_ATENDIMENTO', 'REABERTO')
  AND ('${tecnico:csv}' = '' OR c."tecnicoId" = ANY(string_to_array('${tecnico:csv}', ',')))
  AND ('${servico:csv}' = '' OR os."servicoId" = ANY(string_to_array('${servico:csv}', ',')))
  AND ('${setor:csv}' = '' OR u.setor::text = ANY(string_to_array('${setor:csv}', ',')))
GROUP BY c.id, c."OS", c.descricao, c.status, t.nome, t.sobrenome, u.setor, c."geradoEm"
ORDER BY c."geradoEm" DESC
LIMIT 50;
